content: I forgot to post for the 1 year anniversary of being on HRT (end of January)! Have a photo of me looking a bit tired in a pub last Thursday.

photo.alt: A photograph of me sitting in The Basketmakers Arms in Brighton. I’m wearing a subdued floarl corduroy shirt, a fused glass amulet, and a black button up dress over the top. I’m also wearing cat-eye shaped glasses and a black yoga band.
